cdata.name: Guaranteed Ethurance Token Extra
cdata.desc:
Inschain is an online platform thatworks as a customizableand scalable insurance ecosystem basedon blockchain technology. It aims to transform the traditional insurancemechanism by digitalizing insurance products and modularizing insurance business process.

Guaranteed Ethurance Token Extrais an ERC20-based token used as a medium ofvalue transmission on Inschain, holders can buy products and services and will receive GETXin case of claims.
